    "details": {
      "biography": {
        "value": "<p>The Rootgnaw Queen is the grotesque mother of the rootgnaw grub swarms — a massive root-and-chitin horror that commands the battlefield through brood coordination and a corrupting presence. She does not move quickly but she does not need to; her grub-children swarm at her command and her corruption aura erodes the resolve of nearby heroes. When threatened, she accelerates her brood-spawning, flooding the encounter with fresh minions from the earth beneath her.</p>",
